Thank You from Walmart

I meant to reply sooner, but the day got away from me and I only just sat down for a quiet minute.

I tried that route you suggested last week, and it was much easier than the one I usually take. The path near the trees was calmer, and I finally noticed the little bench by the corner that everyone keeps talking about.

I also followed your idea about keeping a small notebook nearby, and it actually helped me remember the tiny things I would normally forget by dinner.

I am still sorting through the rest of the weekend plans, though. If the weather stays mild, I will probably spend part of the afternoon outside and then tackle the shelf in the hallway that has been leaning to one side for ages.

Also, yes, I found the blue mug. It was behind a stack of folded towels for some reason.

