Walmart values clarity, convenience, and timely access to practical offers. Availability may be limited by response timing and general eligibility review.

Sent to eligible recipients in connection with a promotional thank-you message from Walmart.

I checked the drawer this morning and finally found the spare key tucked inside the little tin with the paper clips.

That made me laugh because I had already looked there twice and somehow missed it both times. I guess I was in too much of a rush earlier in the week and wasn’t really paying attention.

I took your advice and made a short list before starting anything else, and it kept me from bouncing between four different tasks at once. I even finished the plant stand repair before lunch, which honestly surprised me.

The basil on the windowsill looks much healthier now that I remembered to rotate it, and the room feels brighter just from moving a few things around.

I am free later in the afternoon if you still want help sorting those books. I can also bring a couple of empty boxes if that makes things easier.

